Comments: Based on observation, interview and record review, the facility failed to obtain prescribed medications in a timely manner for 2 of 4 sampled residents. This failure resulted in the residents not receiving the medications and placed them at risk of compromised health.  The facility failed to develop and maintain a disaster plan including a place to evacuate residents from the facility, provisions for resident medications and emergency communication plan.  Based on observation, interview and record review, the facility failed to include snacks served on the menu, check food temperature prior to serving, have the diet manual available to staff preparing and serving food as ordered and the diet manual was approved by a dietitian.
